This paper is primarily focused on face detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of learning algorithms and feature representation, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of multi-scale features, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and the paper discusses the performance of the proposed method against state-of-the-art algorithms, which is a common topic in cryptography (cs.CR).
